{title: Highlight Markup}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[Am]Pay attention to the <highlight>highlighted part</highlight> here
[Em]This is normal but <highlight>this stands out</highlight>
[Dm]<highlight>Entire line highlighted for emphasis</highlight>
[Am]Back to normal [Em]text
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[F]<highlight>Remember this line</highlight>
[C]<highlight>And this one too</highlight>
[G]Not this one [Am]though
{end_of_chorus}
